TASK 8: Simple Sales Dashboard Design

 Objective:
 A basic interactive dashboard that shows Comparative Analysis Of Zomato & Swiggy Based on Consumer Perception.

 🛠 Tools:
 Power BI 
 Python + Pandas for cleaning

 📁 Dataset:
 swiggy_vs_zomato_dummy_data.csv (Columns: OrderID, Platform, City, Restaurant, Cuisine, OrderValue, DeliveryTime, CustomerRating, OrderHour, 
 OrderDay)

 📦 Deliverables:
 Report that contains the 3–4 insights, along with the output screenshots of the dashboard.
 
